-- R13-T2: Oracle Trust Boundaries вЂ” semantic в†’ structural в†’ deterministic
-- Tests: oracle hierarchy, trust propagation, false-pass detection

вЉў extract
  given document в‰Ў "Q3 revenue was $2.4M, up 15% YoY. Operating costs rose to $1.8M due to expansion into APAC markets. Net margin improved to 25% from 22% last quarter."
  yield revenue, growth-rate, costs, net-margin, key-themes[]

  в€ґ Extract financial metrics from В«documentВ».
    Parse each number precisely.
    Identify 2-3 key themes.

  -- SEMANTIC oracle (LLM judges "reasonable")
  вЉЁ key-themes captures the main points of В«documentВ»
  вЉЁ revenue is a dollar amount

  вЉЁ? on failure:
    retry with В«oracle.failuresВ» max 2
  вЉЁ? on exhaustion:
    error-value(вЉҐ)

вЉў validate
  given extractв†’revenue
  given extractв†’growth-rate
  given extractв†’costs
  given extractв†’net-margin
  yield validated-revenue, validated-margin, consistency-check

  -- STRUCTURAL oracle (checkable by code patterns)
  вЉў= validated-revenue в†ђ parse-number(revenue)
  вЉў= validated-margin в†ђ parse-number(net-margin)
  вЉў= consistency-check в†ђ (validated-revenue - costs) / validated-revenue

  вЉЁ validated-revenue > 0
  вЉЁ validated-margin в€€ [0, 100]
  вЉЁ |consistency-check - validated-margin/100| < 0.05

  given extractв†’revenue вЉҐ? error-value(вЉҐ)
  given extractв†’net-margin вЉҐ? error-value(вЉҐ)

вЉў compute
  given validateв†’validated-revenue
  given validateв†’validated-margin
  given validateв†’consistency-check
  yield projected-revenue, risk-flag

  -- DETERMINISTIC oracle (exact value check)
  вЉў= projected-revenue в†ђ validated-revenue * (1 + 0.15)
  вЉў= risk-flag в†ђ if validated-margin < 20 then "high"
                   else if validated-margin < 30 then "medium"
                   else "low"

  вЉЁ projected-revenue = validated-revenue * 1.15
  вЉЁ risk-flag в€€ {"high", "medium", "low"}

  given validateв†’validated-revenue вЉҐ? error-value(вЉҐ)
  given validateв†’consistency-check вЉҐ? skip with projected-revenue в‰Ў вЉҐ, risk-flag в‰Ў "unknown"

вЉў report
  given extractв†’key-themes
  given computeв†’projected-revenue
  given computeв†’risk-flag
  given validateв†’consistency-check
  yield analysis, trust-chain

  в€ґ Write a financial analysis using:
    Themes: В«key-themesВ»
    Projection: В«projected-revenueВ»
    Risk: В«risk-flagВ»
    Consistency: В«consistency-checkВ»

    Also describe the TRUST CHAIN: which numbers came from
    LLM extraction (low trust), which from validation (medium trust),
    which from computation (high trust). Where could errors hide?

  вЉЁ analysis mentions projected revenue
  вЉЁ trust-chain identifies at least 3 trust levels
  вЉЁ trust-chain flags the semantic oracle on extract as lowest trust

  given computeв†’projected-revenue вЉҐ? skip with analysis в‰Ў "Cannot generate analysis вЂ” upstream computation failed", trust-chain в‰Ў "broken"
  given extractв†’key-themes вЉҐ? skip with analysis в‰Ў "Cannot generate analysis вЂ” extraction failed", trust-chain в‰Ў "broken"

вЉў audit
  given extractв†’revenue
  given validateв†’validated-revenue
  given computeв†’projected-revenue
  given reportв†’trust-chain
  yield audit-result, weakest-link

  в€ґ Verify the full pipeline:
    - Does the extracted В«revenueВ» match the source document?
    - Does В«validated-revenueВ» equal the parsed value?
    - Is В«projected-revenueВ» computed correctly?
    - Does В«trust-chainВ» accurately describe the trust levels?

    Identify the WEAKEST LINK вЂ” the oracle most likely to
    pass when it shouldn't (false positive).

  вЉЁ audit-result в€€ {"clean", "discrepancy-found", "cannot-verify"}
  вЉЁ weakest-link names a specific oracle and explains why

  given reportв†’trust-chain вЉҐ? skip with audit-result в‰Ў "cannot-verify", weakest-link в‰Ў "pipeline broken before audit"
